, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/28389/', '', 'Orlistat, Viloxazine, Milnacipran, Esketamine', 'St. John''s Wort, Oxitriptan, Viloxazine, Tryptophan, Bupropion, Esketamine', 1767369485);
