, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/28392/', '', 'St. John''s Wort, Oxitriptan, Viloxazine, Tryptophan, Bupropion, Esketamine', 'Ephedrine, Phentermine, Diethylpropion, Mazindol, Mirtazapine', 1767369485);
